Miscellaneous Highlights: Ecuador and Chile are both on five points in the World Cup qualifiers and aim for a win.
Ecuador is on a streak of two consecutive goalless draws.
Chile has only one win in five qualifiers, a 2-0 victory against Peru.
Ecuador's predicted XI includes Dominguez, Preciado, and Sornoza.
Chile's predicted XI includes Cortes, Medel, and Brereton Diaz.
The match is at Rodrigo Paz Delgado Stadium with a 6:30 pm ET kick-off.
The match can be watched on Fanatiz in the US.
